description: Projet de formulation d'un plan de gestion du complexe humide de Guerbès -Senhadja utilisant un processu participatif des populations locales et des ONGs ainsi que des propostion de diminution des pressions et des déffrichement à travers deux projets pil

subproject.corporate outcome: Development plans and programmes integrate environmentally sustainable solutions in a manner that promotes poverty reduction, MDG achievement and low-emission climate-resilient development
subproject.description:
The project joins in the objective of the plan RAMSAR for the rational use of the wet zones within the framework of the sustainable development.
The project will contribute to the development of a plan of management integrated(joined) by the pond overturning of the wet plain of Guerbès.
subproject.gender code: No noticeable contribution to gender equality
subproject.title: Elaborate plan of management
